HEADWORD: Apodyterium
<hw>A*pod`y*te"ri*um</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.,
fr. Gr. <?/, fr. <?/ to strip one's self.]</ety> <fld>(Anc. Arch.)</fld>
